column6: Si bona suscepimus de manu Domini,
column7: If we have received good things from the hand of the Lord,
why should we not endure bad things?
The Lord has given, the Lord has taken away;

column6: sicut Domino placuit, ita factum est:
column7: as it has pleased the Lord, so is it done:
blessed be the name of the Lord.
